MaxWalkSpeed.Description: The Hag move speed (centimetres per second)

TeleportMaxDistance.Description: Max distance from the trap at which the hag can teleport

PhantomTrap_DetectionBuff.Description: Small game effect is widen for phantom traps

PhantomTrap_ActiveTime.Description: Time during which the hag can teleport / the phantom is visible.

PhantomTrap_TriggerAttackTime.Description: The Hag will receive a Score for landing an attack on a Trap Triggerer within this amount of time

PhantomTrap_TeleportAttackTime.Description: The Hag will receive a Score for landing an attack after a Teleport within this amount of time

PhantomTrap_TeleportCooldownDuration.Description: In seconds. Cooldown is only applicable with an addon.

TeleportStunTime.Description: Time during which the hag can't move/attack after a teleport. In seconds. Must be greater than 0.

PhantomTrap_ActivateNotifySurvivorBotsRa.Description: The audible range for survivor bots to detect the trap is activated

PhantomTrap_WipeAwayTime.Description: Time it takes for survivor to wipe away trap
